{"tid":1963425,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【新玩法】梁家輝女兒為愛雀綁帶控制飛行範圍 怕被鷹叼走","createTime":"2020-04-08T06:31:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-08T12:07:04.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"2619acc89f2f4ee0855b40a6f91eebdcd6e49d8a","tid":1963425,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T06:31:02.000Z","msg":"養雀不只是老人的嗜好，有不少年輕人都有養雀，圈中也有不少愛雀之人，當中要數大台小花陳庭欣，家中養有數隻鸚鵡，她與愛雀們十分親近，也有在社交平台分享自己與愛雀們的日常。<br />\n<br />\n原來影帝梁家輝的女兒梁穎晨（Chloe）最近亦成為雀仔主人，她今天在社交平台貼出愛雀的相片和短片，但卻發現雀仔身上多了一條綁着身體的布帶，Chloe特地講到綁雀原因：「本來應該讓牠自由的飛來飛去玩，但是一天比一天晚回來，突然有一天郵差先生開車到我們家門口說來送鳥，原來小鳥認得郵差叔叔，所以就飛到他身上了。我們怕將來會有人覺得牠太可愛把牠帶走，那怎麼辦？所以我特地做了一個flying harness給牠，每天跟牠散步讓他在安全範圍裏飛。」而在外國成長的Chloe再以英語補充指：「牠看到皮帶（flying harness）感到很興奮，就算戴上綁帶，仍可完美地飛翔。」她又指因為家附近有很多鷹會飛來，怕愛雀飛上樹會有危險，故此決定為牠綁上布帶，控制牠可飛行的範圍。<br />\n<br />\n從Chloe公開的短片中，的確看到牠的雀可以飛行，而雀仔步行玩跟足球時，一度「踩波車」，未知是否與牠身體有綁帶、導致未調適到平衡有關。有網民言給Chloe，指從未見過雀仔身上戴綁帶，Chloe親自回覆指「是超級安全和舒適」，並指很多雀仔飼主用的腳鏈會很容易傷到雀仔的腳，Chloe稱自己上網搜集資料才做出來的。<br />\n<br />\nChloe約在1個月前開始公開與愛雀的合照，並透露雀仔每天都會飛出去玩，當感到悶時便會回家找她求安慰，而雀仔與Chloe的愛犬相處融洽，經常結伴。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200407/large/1586268783_c095.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200407%2Flarge%2F1586268783_c095.jpg&h=155327c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200407/YX4KU64W44V33KTMC3IMYXQX6Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200407%2FYX4KU64W44V33KTMC3IMYXQX6Y%2F&d=LgTIxyFtuo0acoW68XVTBUlZDiKRLpOq3%2FNqhGVOPOo%3D&h=b635dc90\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200407%2FYX4KU64W44V33KTMC3IMYXQX6Y%2F&h=8e4dfda6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200407/YX4KU64W44V33KTMC3IMYXQX6Y/</a>"},{"pid":"7d33bae515a0b65b33dae1f7a7edab56020819d5","tid":1963425,"uid":213877,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T06:32:25.000Z","msg":"老豆大巴錢，無左再買過囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc2c02c03f18e7b728063120e8e9504061912203","tid":1963425,"uid":261849,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T06:33:18.000Z","msg":"幫佢個女綁條帶啦⋯⋯<br />\n好安全同舒適<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b8b0d477a60c75a0ea74a352d132d198328e8ff","tid":1963425,"uid":3873,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T06:42:15.000Z","msg":"唔係通常綁腳架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aebc2a4dbf9918c5453d556980f16b6baf80f49","tid":1963425,"uid":269061,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T06:45:35.000Z","msg":"條廢老上大陸電視，開頭大dee 上身。"},{"pid":"3c93e6d82ed9216d818c019dd0c48aa995c7f2b4","tid":1963425,"uid":118120,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2b8b0d477a60c75a0ea74a352d132d198328e8ff","tid":1963425,"uid":3873,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T06:42:15.000Z","msg":"唔係通常綁腳架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T06:46:26.000Z","msg":"綁身體冇咁傷, <br />\n綁腳d 雀依然會博命想飛出去, 跟住搞到隻腳好傷"},{"pid":"da6583706ba937b572223e52d0867425c2ab250e","tid":1963425,"uid":66365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T06:46:29.000Z","msg":"想做隻雀俾佢綁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfb1b767d7f67162af0d3ced2a36332e81e106fd","tid":1963425,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T06:48:16.000Z","msg":"飛行繩不嬲都有 要隻雀好信任先套得上"},{"pid":"a51c0a71170872c733d890ba6aced5cf2ecf